<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Students may notice:</p>
<ul>
      <li>There are 12 eggs.</li>
      <li>There are 2 groups of 6.</li>
      <li>I see 6 groups of 2.</li>
    </ul>
<p>Students may wonder:</p>
<ul>
      <li>How many eggs would be in two cartons?</li>
      <li>Are there other equal groups that I don’t see?</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


