    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>The purpose of this warm-up is to elicit ideas students have about objects arranged in an array, which will be useful when students arrange equal groups into arrays in a later activity. While students may notice and wonder many things about this image, ideas around arrangement and equal groups are the important discussion points. When students notice the arrangement of the eggs they look for and make use of structure (MP7).</p>
